    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-08-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-08-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="1556"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1556">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 701.5212/52a.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Special Agent <persName type="to">Carothers</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 10, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Please telegraph for Spanish Ambassador any news you have of Señor Zapico,
                    confidential agent of Spain, of whom nothing has been heard for a month.<note
                        n="97" xml:id="d1556fn97">See telegrams of May 20 and 21, <ref
                            target="#pg_1039">p. 1039</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Osborne.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
